@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_agunwh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.95 / v2 + 0.29) - wp.abs(v1 + 0.26)))
    v2 = v2
    v0 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.41 / v1 + 0.16) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.31)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.55 * v0 + 0.62)) * v2)
    data[tid] = v0
